  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“There’s no shame in fear, <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">my father</a> told me, what matters is how we face it.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_6\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 6\">Chapter 6</a>, Jon I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403115421\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 100/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 395/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 17/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 517/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.783      1 -total\n 77.11%    4.459      1 Template:Ref\n 53.35%    3.085      1 Template:Ref/core\n 21.77%    1.259      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:10726-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403115421 and revision id 217724\n -->\n",
